timeline.bodyText:
Minor change required here.  Based on updates to DSpace/dspace-angular#825 , this sitemapStem should be updated to just be:
String sitemapStem = uiURLStem + "/sitemap";
The reason is that, at the UI level, the sitemapsEndpoint has no meaning. It's only valid for the REST API.  This is needed, to ensure that the sitemap files are available at the root level of the UI (e.g. http://localhost:4000/sitemap_index.xml , http://localhost:4000/sitemap0.xml)

